    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hand-held tools, typically comprising a hardwood or plastic rolling device mounted to a handle, used to flatten, press, or obscure the seams between connected strips of material. Commonly utilized, for example, by wallpaper hangers, tailors, seamstresses, quilters, and leather workers.</Note_Text>
